    261 233 │         "description": "Phase context:\n\n# Feed Search And Practice Context\n\nThe feed is the primary app experience. It loads the authenticated user's steps, applies search filters and sort order, renders a virtualized video feed, records views, and records practice.\n\nSearch behavior is fully specified in `REWRITE_SPEC.md` section 10. Practice duplicate prevention is based on local day and optional collection/session ID.\n\nGoal:\n\nImplement the main `/feed` page with virtualized video cards and step actions.\n\nImplementation:\n\n1. Create `/feed` page.\n2. Query authenticated user's steps.\n3. Apply current search/filter/sort.\n4. Render a virtualized list of feed cards.\n5. Scale primary video height to feed width using stored video dimensions.\n6. Cap video height around `60vh`.\n7. Mount/play videos only when visible using intersection detection or virtualization visibility.\n8. Feed card displays:\n   - Primary video.\n   - Step name.\n   - Tags.\n   - Variation button with count if variations exist.\n   - Practice action.\n   - Options menu.\n9. Variation button opens overlay feed of related variations.\n10. Options menu includes:\n    - Copy link.\n    - Show variations when available.\n    - Edit.\n    - Cancel/close.\n11. Edit opens inline edit modal.\n\nTracer/phase plan:\n\n1. Tracer: `/feed` lists owned steps with primary video card.\n2. Add search/filter/sort integration.\n3. Add virtualization/intersection playback and stable video sizing.\n4. Add tags, variation modal, practice action, options menu.\n5. Wire copy link and inline edit entry.\n\nLikely files:\n\n- Create `app/(authenticated)/feed/page.tsx`.\n- Create `components/feed/steps-feed.tsx`.\n- Create `components/feed/feed-step-card.tsx`.\n- Create `components/feed/step-actions.tsx`.\n- Create `components/feed/options-menu.tsx`.\n- Create `components/steps/step-tags.tsx`.\n- Create `components/steps/variation-feed-modal.tsx`.\n- `app/(authenticated)/feed/page.tsx`\n- `components/feed/steps-feed.tsx`\n- `components/feed/feed-step-card.tsx`\n- `components/feed/step-actions.tsx`\n- `components/feed/options-menu.tsx`\n- `components/steps/step-tags.tsx`\n- `components/steps/variation-feed-modal.tsx`\n- `tests/components/feed.test.tsx`\n\nVerification:\n\nRun:\n\n```bash\nnpm test -- --run\nnpm run typecheck\nnpm run lint\n```\n\nManual checks:\n\n- Feed shows all owned steps by default.\n- Search changes update feed order/results.\n- Videos render at stable responsive sizes.\n- Variation modal shows only related variations.\n- Options menu copies the public link and opens inline edit.\n\nUnresolved questions:\n\n- Which virtualization package should be used, if any?\n\nSource files:\n\n- Task: .agents/tasks/5 - feed search and practice/3 - build virtualized feed and step actions.md\n- Plan: .agents/tasks/5 - feed search and practice/3 - build virtualized feed and step actions.plan.md\n- Context: .agents/tasks/5 - feed search and practice/context.md",
