    313 277 │         "description": "Phase context:\n\n# Sessions And Historical Practice Context\n\nSessions are modeled in the legacy app but active Vue pages currently render placeholders. The rewrite should restore the intended behavior unless product direction explicitly removes sessions. These tasks assume sessions are restored.\n\nSessions are owned, named collections of step IDs. Historical practice is derived from step `practiceRecords` grouped by `startOfDay`.\n\nGoal:\n\nBuild `/sessions` with saved sessions and historical practice groups.\n\nImplementation:\n\n1. Create `/sessions` page.\n2. Query owned practice sessions.\n3. Add `Add session` button.\n4. `Add session` calls `createPracticeSession` with defaults:\n   - `locked: false`\n   - `steps: []`\n   - `name: Practice {dd MMM}`\n5. Render saved sessions as cards:\n   - Session name.\n   - Number of selected steps.\n   - Link to `/sessions/[sessionId]`.\n6. Query historical practice days from step practice records.\n7. Render historical practice cards:\n   - Date label.\n   - Count of unique practiced steps.\n   - Link to `/historical-sessions/[startOfDay]`.\n8. Sort saved sessions and historical days newest first.\n\nTracer/phase plan:\n\n1. Tracer: `/sessions` lists owned practice sessions.\n2. Add create default session button.\n3. Add historical practice grouping from step records.\n4. Sort both sections newest first; add tests.\n\nLikely files:\n\n- Create `app/(authenticated)/sessions/page.tsx`.\n- Create `components/sessions/session-card.tsx`.\n- Create `components/sessions/sessions-list.tsx`.\n- Create `components/sessions/historical-session-card.tsx`.\n- `app/(authenticated)/sessions/page.tsx`\n- `components/sessions/session-card.tsx`\n- `components/sessions/sessions-list.tsx`\n- `components/sessions/historical-session-card.tsx`\n- `tests/components/sessions-list.test.tsx`\n\nVerification:\n\nRun:\n\n```bash\nnpm test -- --run\nnpm run typecheck\nnpm run lint\n```\n\nManual checks:\n\n- Add session creates a session with default name.\n- Saved sessions show step counts.\n- Historical practice days appear from practice records.\n- Links navigate to detail pages.\n\nUnresolved questions:\n\n- Should default session name use browser locale or fixed app locale?\n\nSource files:\n\n- Task: .agents/tasks/7 - sessions and historical practice/1 - implement sessions list.md\n- Plan: .agents/tasks/7 - sessions and historical practice/1 - implement sessions list.plan.md\n- Context: .agents/tasks/7 - sessions and historical practice/context.md",
